{"id":675415,"date":[{"year":1984,"month":5,"day":28}],"page":"5","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"77","ytitle":"","mtitle":"迎上海解放卅五周年","ftitle":"","authors":["辛笛"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛笛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放同歌卅五年，烽烟散尽作炊烟；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织来锦绣工农乐，听去弦歌子弟贤；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖海园林葱郁郁，仁人志士意拳拳:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常将有日思无日，还向丰碑酹九泉。"}]}